<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Als <expan>vorczeite<ex>n</ex></expan> der
                            <expan>hoch<ex>geporn</ex></expan> fürst und
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, <expan>margr<ex>af</ex></expan> Jost von
                                <expan>Merh<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, selig, den
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ir hab und kauffmanschaft in der stat czu
                        Prünne <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> hat, darümb Lucz
                                <expan>Steinling<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> czu
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gned<ex>igen</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, des kunigs von
                            <expan>Beh<ex>eim</ex></expan>
<expan>durchleuhtik<ex>eit</ex></expan>, <expan>czekume<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        maint, <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                            <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> burger gen <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re<ex>n</ex></expan>, des <expan>k<ex>ünigs</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> günstige hilff und
                            <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> gütlich beweisen wöllet, ob den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dieselb ir habe
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>golte<ex>n</ex></expan> und gekert
                                <expan>werde<ex>n</ex></expan> möht. Und tut darynne etc. Als etc.
                        Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>a</ex>to</expan>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Dorothee.</ab>
</div>
